---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="TAFF | DenArt Media" description="DenArt body painting studio featured on TAFF (Prosieben)">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6 bg-deepest">
    <a href="/in_media/" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-gold hover:text-brand-gold-hover mb-8">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
      </svg>
      Back to Media
    </a>

    <article>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">TAFF</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-8">Prosieben | TV, Germany</p>

      <div class="aspect-video mb-8 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-900">
        <iframe 
          src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/50483806" 
          class="w-full h-full"
          frameborder="0" 
          allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" 
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>A profile piece shot while I did a live body painting in public. I painted a reproduction of Salvador Dali's painting Gala and the Tigers.</p>
        <p>This piece was aired on German TV network Prosieben. The show is called TAFF.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
